## Technical Assessment

HFAT-X10 is a unified multi-domain flow governance architecture designed to coordinate airflow, thermal energy, hydraulics, information transfer, communications, and mission resources across the PI220 ecosystem. Integrated with AFAT, X2M, IRAS-X, STARFRAME, NEO CORE NODE, and STARFORCE GRID, it functions as the primary optimization layer for future autonomous aerospace operations.

